    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In fact, our city was, so to say, the, the marketplace as well as the commercial center and the administrative center for a very large, agrarian area.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Children would be sent by their parents-- other than the professional element or the gentry, military officers, et cetera-- would go to the, the required four elementary grades or six elementary grades.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then they would, of course, become part of the-- of the real struggle to maintain their existence.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so the relationship of, of the Jews and the non-Jews was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] made up of, of this primitive, religious, and illiterate [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] aura of, of the area.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- so that although that you would find that there were Jews who had relationships with non-Jews, some even quite close, certainly at the level of the thin layer of very assimilated Jews and professionals and the bankers, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there were pretty close relationships and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and maybe business partnerships.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But there was a wall separating the two communities that could not be penetrated and could not be broken down, even at the level of the-- of the assimilated Jews, the social [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] life [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] which-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] again, you know, Jews, in, in a sense, imitated the Hungarian gentry at that level.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Nonetheless, they were separate, basically.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] A very interesting story of a-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it's a kind of interesting historical vignette.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
